{"tid":2320040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★「永久離港」提取強積金申請按季大減逾兩成","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:15:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a88af8cd3ca7245572718407bbb522cddf94f306","tid":2320040,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"強制性公積金計劃管理局發表數據指，截至今年6月底，以「永久離港」為理由提取強積金的申請由去年第4季的8,400宗，減至今年首季的7,600宗，次季更減至僅6,000宗，宗數按季大減逾兩成，創過去5個季度低位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201210/bkn-20201210205932567-1210_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201210%2Fbkn-20201210205932567-1210_00842_001.html&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=2b6867a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201210/bkn-20201210205932567-1210_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"40bf538edcb6169681b892db9fad32454868ba1c","tid":2320040,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nnone移民？？？？"},{"pid":"c1785b5093271d1fb9b6528613cf15878bb9e312","tid":2320040,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"以永久離港為理由提取MPF的金額亦持續大跌，從去年未季高峰時的14.35億元，跌至今年首季的12.95億元，次季僅報9.9億元，按季急降24%。"},{"pid":"38f78611a2a79c44203b597cfd143b90bb95dabe","tid":2320040,"uid":288505,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"唔撚批就趺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c263d9a281c941bf67641c62ebc2a43cc9d795b","tid":2320040,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"話左bno visa唔批<br />\n要bc先批<br />\n<br />\n自然無人申